---
title: Comforting Double Chorizo & Veggie Traybake with Parmesan Cheese & Herby Mayo
description: Mild chorizo adds instant charm to a trayful of veggies in this no-fuss recipe, imparting a lovely salty and smokey flavour. Along with the creamy herb mayo, the sweetness from the pumpkin works to balance out the richness of the dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6594a1f6b6e284551035ad35-08cf78ea.jpeg
